    "products.header.desc": "Explore our collection of handcrafted pieces, carefully shaped in the Grand Bazaar.",
    "product1.fulltype": "Gold Necklace / 14K Gold Plated Sterling Silver",
    "product1.desc": "A delicate chain adorned with hand-sculpted floral motifs, available in 14K gold or 14K gold plated sterling silver. Each petal is individually shaped by hand, bringing a touch of nature\u2019s elegance to everyday wear. As every piece is handcrafted individually rather than mass-produced, slight variations in weight, dimensions and form may occur \u2014 these differences are a natural part of the process and make each piece truly one of a kind. If you\u2019d like, we can tailor this design to your vision \u2014 whether it\u2019s a different stone, an adjusted size, or an entirely new form, we\u2019re happy to work with you to create something uniquely yours.",
    "product2.fulltype": "14K Gold / 14K Gold Plated 925 Sterling Silver Ring",
    "product2.desc": "A 14K gold plated 925 sterling silver signet ring with a genuine ruby at its centre, framed in a gypsy-star set with a lab-grown diamond on each side. The flush set keeps the stones secure and smooth against the skin \u2014 a ring that quietly sparkles through your everyday life, from morning coffee to evening out. Understated yet unmistakable. Each ring is made to order in our workshop, with the finish and stone placement executed entirely by hand. As every piece is individually crafted rather than mass-produced, slight variations in weight, dimensions and form may occur \u2014 these differences make each ring uniquely yours. If you\u2019d like, we can tailor this design to your preference \u2014 a different stone, a different size, or an entirely new form.",
    "product3.fulltype": "14K Gold / 14K Gold Plated 925 Sterling Silver Necklace",
    "product3.desc": "A personalised initial pendant on a fine chain, available in 14K gold or 14K gold plated 925 sterling silver. Your chosen letter is carefully shaped by hand. Wear your own initial or that of someone you love \u2014 a quiet, personal statement that sits close to the heart. As every piece is individually crafted rather than mass-produced, slight variations in weight, dimensions and form may occur \u2014 these differences make each piece uniquely yours. If you\u2019d like, we can tailor this design to your preference \u2014 a different font style, chain length, or added stone detail.",
    "product4.fulltype": "Gold Station Necklace",
    "product4.desc": "A modern station necklace with delicate gold beads spaced along a fine chain. Clean, minimal and effortlessly versatile \u2014 designed to be layered with other necklaces or worn on its own for a subtle everyday look. The kind of piece that goes with everything and quietly elevates whatever you pair it with.",
    "product5.fulltype": "Rose Gold Pendant Necklace",
    "product5.desc": "A circular pendant in warm rose gold, adorned with coloured gemstone butterflies. The ring symbolises eternity while the butterfly cluster brings a sense of lightness and movement.",
    "product6.fulltype": "Gold Earrings with Emerald",
    "product6.desc": "Diamond-set bow earrings with emerald drop pendants in rose gold. The delicate bow motif, encrusted with sparkling stones, suspends a lush emerald cabochon — a playful yet refined pairing that captures the elegance of Ottoman court jewellery.",
    "product7.fulltype": "Gold Pendant Necklace with Sapphire",
    "product7.desc": "A protective eye pendant in fine gold with hand-set sapphires at its centre, framed by a granulated bezel. Rooted in Anatolian tradition, the nazar motif is reimagined here as a modern talisman — a piece that carries meaning as beautifully as it carries light.",
    "product8.fulltype": "Gold ID Bracelet",
    "product8.desc": "A personalised gold chain bracelet featuring a hand-engraved nameplate and gemstone accents. The bold curb chain meets delicate detail — a contemporary take on the classic künye, crafted to carry a name close to the heart.",
    "product9.fulltype": "Gold & Baroque Pearl Pendant",
    "product9.desc": "A hand-sculpted golden butterfly rests upon a luminous baroque pearl, creating a pendant that feels born from nature itself. Each pearl's unique form inspires the placement of the butterfly — no two pieces are ever alike, making this a truly one-of-a-kind creation.",
    "product10.fulltype": "Gold Chain Bracelet with Heart",
    "product10.desc": "A gold curb-chain bracelet centred with a hand-cut heart motif and accented by a coloured gemstone. The heart carries a hand-engraved initial, transforming a bold chain into something deeply personal — a love letter worn on the wrist.",
    "product11.fulltype": "Gold Hoop Earrings with Pearl",
    "product11.desc": "Sculpted gold hoops with hand-engraved leaf detailing, each suspending a lustrous freshwater pearl. The organic texture of the gold and the natural glow of the pearl create a harmony of warmth and light — effortlessly elegant for any occasion.",
    "product12.fulltype": "Gold Pendant Necklace with Gemstones",
    "product12.desc": "A circular gold pendant enclosing a miniature garden of hand-painted enamel roses in deep ruby and emerald tones. Hung from a substantial chain and crowned with a tiny ruby accent, this piece is a wearable tribute to Istanbul's famed tulip-era gardens.",
    "product13.fulltype": "Rose Gold Necklace with Ruby",
    "product13.desc": "A diamond-encrusted bow in rose gold suspends a vivid ruby drop, creating a piece that balances femininity with brilliance. The bow motif — a symbol of connection and celebration — is rendered with the precision of Grand Bazaar master setters.",
