    "intro.subtitle": "\u0130stanbul'da El Yap\u0131m\u0131",
    "intro.title": "Gelene\u011fin Zamans\u0131z Zarafetle Bulu\u015fmas\u0131",
    "intro.p1": "Rosary par\u00e7alar\u0131, nesillerdir s\u00fcregelen kuyumculuk gelene\u011finin ya\u015fad\u0131\u011f\u0131 Kapal\u0131\u00e7ar\u015f\u0131'da \u00f6zenle el yap\u0131m\u0131 olarak \u00fcretilir. Alt\u0131n ve do\u011fal ta\u015flarla, hem zamans\u0131z hem ki\u015fiye \u00f6zel hissettiren par\u00e7alar \u00fcretiyoruz.",
    "intro.p2": "Her par\u00e7a bir hikaye anlat\u0131r \u2014 niyetin, \u00f6zenin ve el eme\u011finin sessiz g\u00fczelli\u011finin.",
